    "conclusion": "A non-inferiority claim against the append-only baseline is only warranted when all three gates\u2014scheduler viability, artifact quality within the 0.10 margin, and observability separation\u2014are satisfied simultaneously. The protocol explicitly denies credit to any attempt that fails one gate and compensates with another.",
